  "monster": {
    "title": "Muchiol.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Muchiol has a skeletal green body and a great mass of hair. It stinks of death.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 136     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: ++++     </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: ++++ +++  </lightgrey>                \n<darkgrey>    rF: ...     </darkgrey><lightgrey>   rC: +..      </lightgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: +        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\n\n\nYou have about 22% to hit with the +8 morningstar of Frustration and 3% to hit with your bite.\nIt has about 63% to hit you.\n\nAttack                 Max Damage  \nSting: venomous touch  37 + venom  \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.\n\nIt is currently targeting the balrug.\n\nThis monster has been temporarily summoned to this location. If angered it will immediately vanish, yielding no experience or items; it is incapable of using stairs.",
